sequenceDiagram
    participant KFP as KFP Backend /<br/>DSP API Server
    participant SDK as KFP Python SDK /<br/>Pipeline UI
    participant MLMD as MLMD gRPC Server<br/>8080/TCP gRPC/HTTP2<br/>Optional TLS (SSLConfig)
    participant DB as MySQL/PostgreSQL<br/>3306 or 5432/TCP<br/>Optional SSL

    Note over KFP,DB: Flow 1: Pipeline Run Metadata Recording

    KFP->>MLMD: PutExecution(execution, artifacts,<br/>events, contexts)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2, Optional TLS
    activate MLMD
    MLMD->>DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION<br/>INSERT/UPDATE entities<br/>Username/password auth
    activate DB
    DB-->>MLMD: Transaction committed
    deactivate DB
    MLMD-->>KFP: PutExecutionResponse<br/>(execution_id, artifact_ids)
    deactivate MLMD

    KFP->>MLMD: PutArtifacts(artifacts)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2
    activate MLMD
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT/UPDATE artifacts
    activate DB
    DB-->>MLMD: OK
    deactivate DB
    MLMD-->>KFP: PutArtifactsResponse<br/>(artifact_ids)
    deactivate MLMD

    KFP->>MLMD: PutEvents(events)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2
    activate MLMD
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT events<br/>(artifact-execution links)
    activate DB
    DB-->>MLMD: OK
    deactivate DB
    MLMD-->>KFP: PutEventsResponse
    deactivate MLMD

    Note over SDK,DB: Flow 2: Lineage Graph Query

    SDK->>MLMD: GetLineageSubgraph(query)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2, Optional TLS
    activate MLMD
    MLMD->>DB: SELECT with lineage traversal<br/>Configurable depth & direction
    activate DB
    DB-->>MLMD: Result set (entities, edges)
    deactivate DB
    MLMD-->>SDK: LineageSubgraph<br/>(artifacts, executions,<br/>contexts, events)
    deactivate MLMD

    SDK->>MLMD: GetArtifactsByContext(context_id)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2
    activate MLMD
    MLMD->>DB: SELECT artifacts<br/>JOIN attributions
    activate DB
    DB-->>MLMD: Artifact records
    deactivate DB
    MLMD-->>SDK: GetArtifactsByContextResponse<br/>(artifacts[])
    deactivate MLMD
